      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapists just tell u to try harder or breathe or something. i've done all that. it doesnt change the fact that the loop is always there. it's like a glitch in the system. no matter what i do, the outcome is always the same. the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just... break it. to make it stop for good.",
